{"tid":1913044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡多13人確診　包括新航一機組人員","createTime":"2020-03-06T13:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T00:03:56.000Z","uid":41818,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"01888f513246de757a61c78110aad73dc05502a9","tid":1913044,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"新加坡多13人感染新型冠狀病毒，累計確診個案達130宗。新增患者中，有兩宗是輸入病例，其中一名47歲男子，是新加坡航空的機組人員，上月中至本月初到過南非及法國，他自出現病徵後已沒有上班，另一名37歲女子曾到過德國。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有9宗新個案與裕廊戰備軍人協會俱樂部，上月中一個私人晚宴有關，至今這個感染群組已有17人確診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1271966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1271966&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=abc9b36e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1271966</a>"},{"pid":"ca370c4bde41856f9c4c75873eb1d7f8989a8d62","tid":1913044,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:43:16.000Z","msg":"坡狗加油<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c83987440676ab6e0c29848a2cf69711b8fd4612","tid":1913044,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471c490b5a16d658c5409211f0a2707521fb30ad","tid":1913044,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c83987440676ab6e0c29848a2cf69711b8fd4612","tid":1913044,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc6b1a91a11886c6770d76e0f4e71ed7030b428","tid":1913044,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/20/OPz5eM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F12%2F20%2FOPz5eM.png&h=fef7be3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b7486120a48d424e8687c03a179c91399ccca54","tid":1913044,"uid":4243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"另外，有9宗新個案與裕廊戰備軍人協會俱樂部，上月中一個私人晚宴有關，至今這個感染群組已有17人確診。<br />\n<br />\n哈哈, 香港"},{"pid":"618577b222ea89080b752ef43c91dbfbde8ee582","tid":1913044,"uid":103050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:48:31.000Z","msg":"坡狗加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亞洲人唔可以俾鬼佬睇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid